1.Install Docker on windows

2.pull selenium/stanalone chrome driver

3.docker run -p 4444:4444 --name seleniumgrid selenium/standalone-chrome
(use -p or leave it it will run in background)

4.http://localhost:4444

5.Go to sesssion manager.

6.it will ask for password

7.password is secret.

8.you can see the test in the vnc player.

